{"tid":1882601,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中央政府向湖北捐贈《建軍大業》電影 為抗疫打氣","createTime":"2020-02-16T11:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T12:00:55.000Z","uid":41343,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a725ea1bc322a56044639fbadd845239258ce4","tid":1882601,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"近日，中國電影頻道節目中心精心組織甄選出60部反映時代精神風貌的正能量優秀國產影片，在抗疫期間捐贈給湖北。<br />\n<br />\n其中，向湖北廣播電視台、武漢廣播電視台捐贈的30部影片主要為《建軍大業》、《老師&middot;好》、《破風》、《閃光少女》、《熱乾麵的味道》等院線電影精品；向武漢方艙醫院捐贈的30部影片均為《紅色之子&middot;單刀赴會》、《小狗奶瓶》、《龍形俠影黃澄可》等收視好評的電影頻道出品影片。<br />\n<br />\n捐贈影片於今日起陸續在湖北廣播電視台6個頻道（湖北經視、湖北綜合、湖北影視、湖北壟上、湖北教育、湖北生活）和武漢廣播電視台3個頻道（科技生活、武漢文體、武漢少兒）及武漢方艙醫院播出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/02/15/EN2002150007.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2FEN2002150007.htm&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbkzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=349f03ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2020/02/15/EN2002150007.htm</a>"},{"pid":"04b464cea7f8bfa2c746b96521f5ba7cc662971c","tid":1882601,"uid":41524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"嘩!!感謝黨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a7d0008b0a7fc237c0aa67ce19261ba646a7bd","tid":1882601,"uid":194326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nno comment"},{"pid":"5002cbc365cd36f00b575b5920943d80fa539af6","tid":1882601,"uid":33456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"電影抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"h